title: The Great British Bake Off 2019 finalists: which bakers are competing in the final tonight - and who has left so far?
text:
The tenth series of The Great British Bake Off serves as a special anniversary season this year.

And there’s been a lot of questions over this latest season. Where have all the middle-aged bakers gone? Are the technical challenges too hard? Has it become more mean-spirited? Certainly it feels as though this season has been fashioned in the mould of Paul Hollywood, a man all but allergic to the notion of charm.

Still the three who have won a place in tonight’s final all deserve their places. But who is left in the competition? And what skills are they bringing to the final..?
